Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.14,0:00:02.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Pain that won’t heal
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.16,0:00:03.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sadness you feel
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.98,0:00:06.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Scars that just refuse to fade\Nfrom memory
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.20,0:00:09.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes the burden’s too much\Nfor one to bear
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.05,0:00:12.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t give up on me,\Nplease don’t turn me away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.52,0:00:14.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.92,0:00:18.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll hold your hand in mine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.70,0:00:25.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Will I lose my hold on her someday?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.93,0:00:32.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Will her smile fade in a flood of tears\NOr can I keep the fears at bay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.44,0:00:37.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Echoing, distant voices wither into silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.07,0:00:41.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But there is one thing that\Nwill never ever age…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.48,0:00:46.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My love for you is timeless
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.89,0:00:47.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Pain that won’t heal
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.85,0:00:49.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sadness you feel
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.64,0:00:51.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Smiles with hearts’ bitterness replaced
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.79,0:00:53.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,“I’ll never smile again”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.30,0:00:54.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,“I’ll never let love in”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.96,0:00:57.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t ever say such things to me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.45,0:01:00.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A future we cannot see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.64,0:01:03.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All happenings\NFind meaning in the story
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.32,0:01:08.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In time the clouds will clear away,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.14,0:01:12.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,so just stay, please stay with me…\NWhoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.20,0:01:17.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who are we to pass through you?\NWhoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.39,0:01:20.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That answer will find you someday
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.40,0:01:35.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My body feels heavy…\NMy legs…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.24,0:01:40.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t raise my arm either…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.95,0:01:48.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, I guess…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.76,0:01:52.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,the end is nearing for my time\Nas a Quincy…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.75,0:01:56.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That’s right!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.96,0:02:02.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If I’m the first one here,\NI could rescue Rukia myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.57,0:02:07.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I bet Ichigo wants to\Nsave her himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.59,0:02:10.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If I did that, he’d be ticked off.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.27,0:02:38.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I bear no ill feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.24,0:02:42.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,However, for the sake of the peace,\NI’ve no choice but to eliminate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.58,0:02:46.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Cry, Suzumushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.58,0:03:00.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me, Ryoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.61,0:03:04.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is the end of\Na senseless battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.25,0:03:10.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sleep. Your battle will soon be over.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.30,0:03:13.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,To advance from “Shikai” to “Bankai”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.63,0:03:16.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,typically requires well over\Nten years of training,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.20,0:03:17.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,even for those with talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.32,0:03:23.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,However, you must achieve\Nthe “Bankai” in three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.20,0:03:32.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is that strange doll?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.55,0:03:33.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tenshintai.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.60,0:03:38.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It is one of the Stealth Squad’s\Nmost important specialized spirit tools.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.60,0:03:43.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It forcibly draws out the zanpaku-to’s\Ntrue form and materializes it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.83,0:03:46.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Uh? I don’t quite get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.59,0:03:49.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How’s that thing necessary\Nfor the Bankai training?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.12,0:03:51.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What is necessary for the Shikai
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.77,0:03:54.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,is a dialogue\Nand harmony with the zanpaku-to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.14,0:03:55.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.90,0:03:59.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,instead of us entering\Nthe world of the zanpaku-to,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.24,0:04:01.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,what is necessary for the “Bankai”
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.96,0:04:04.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,is the “materialization”\Nand “submission” of the zanpaku-to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.76,0:04:10.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,“Materialization” refers to\Nsummoning the zanpaku-to into our world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.08,0:04:14.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, several years of training\Nare required for this,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.06,0:04:17.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but you, even though\Nit ended in a draw,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.89,0:04:20.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,fought on equal footing\Nwith Kenpachi Zaraki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.49,0:04:26.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So in actuality, you may have\Nalready reached the "materialization"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.64,0:04:29.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,or a comparable level as I see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.17,0:04:32.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.88,0:04:39.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It seems you recall an instance…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.77,0:04:42.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you stab this with Zangetsu,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.97,0:04:46.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,it can forcibly bring it into\Nthe “materialized” state.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.96,0:04:50.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, we can bring\Nthe zanpaku-to into this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.04,0:04:51.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,However…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.25,0:04:56.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Using this method, the “materialization”\Nis limited to three days!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.96,0:05:00.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,During that period, you must defeat\Nthe “materialized” Zangetsu
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.76,0:05:02.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and force him into submission.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.17,0:05:04.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you cannot…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.56,0:05:09.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I won’t ask about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.34,0:05:14.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If this is the only way…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.81,0:05:17.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then I’ve got to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.86,0:05:30.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Seems you have recovered\Nquite a bit, Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.54,0:05:32.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dude!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.21,0:05:35.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You heard our conversation?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.52,0:05:37.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.34,0:05:40.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll leave the fighting methods to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.17,0:05:42.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Can you start right away?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.88,0:05:43.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.52,0:05:58.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the heck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.12,0:06:04.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Among these, only one…\Nis the true me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.09,0:06:09.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That is the only one\Nthat can defeat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.31,0:06:13.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you wish to force me\Ninto submission,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.00,0:06:15.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,find it before I kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.32,0:06:17.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.82,0:06:20.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Slay me if you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.40,0:06:48.24,OS,Default,0000,0000,0000,,FOUR
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.56,0:06:51.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Greetings, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.37,0:06:56.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It is I, Squad Four, Third Seat,\NYasochika Iemura.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.25,0:06:58.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What? You don’t know me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.85,0:07:02.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You may have seen me here,\Nor over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.94,0:07:07.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Since it seems some of you\Nare not familiar with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.50,0:07:11.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,as an introduction,\NI wish to disclose my medical journal
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.36,0:07:15.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,that chronicles our Squad Four’s\Nstrenuous activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.84,0:07:18.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Hey, hurry it up!\N– Reporting!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.35,0:07:20.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Lately, due to the recent\NRyoka disturbance,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.67,0:07:23.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,our Squad Four station\Nis in daily chaos!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.05,0:07:28.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Especially, with the large number of\Nthose louts from Squad 11 hospitalized.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.99,0:07:31.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No! I mean, those gentlemen…\Nit has kept us very busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.21,0:07:33.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, yesterday evening,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.87,0:07:39.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,both the Squad 13 and 8 captains\Nrequested to have a Ryoka admitted
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.52,0:07:44.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,so we were forced to implement\Nthe three-shift emergency protocol.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.88,0:07:47.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Things are busy enough as is,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.82,0:07:51.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and on top of this, being asked\Nto admit the Ryoka is just…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.10,0:07:53.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Really, enough is enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.21,0:07:57.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why these defeated Ryoka\Nshould be purposely hospitalized
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.74,0:08:01.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and treated in the first place\Nis completely beyond me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.92,0:08:06.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, the Squad 13’s\NCaptain Ukitake is one thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.41,0:08:09.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but Captain Kyoraku of Squad Eight\Nis always goofing off
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.42,0:08:13.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and chasing after girls’ behinds\Nand with that gaudy attire,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.88,0:08:16.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,always snoozing when\Nsomething comes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.43,0:08:20.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How can someone like that\Nbecome a captain, while I…!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.50,0:08:23.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.08,0:08:27.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Just now, we received a request\Nfrom Captain Tosen of Squad Nine
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.52,0:08:30.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,to admit one Ryoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.92,0:08:32.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.44,0:08:35.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.76,0:08:39.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You were thinking out loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.06,0:08:52.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,However, I have the deepest respect\Nfor Captain Kyoraku.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.42,0:08:54.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In light of these points!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.53,0:08:57.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He who was held by the Ryoka…!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.11,0:09:01.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,was physically and mentally subjugated\Nby those Ryoka
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.43,0:09:05.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and had no choice but to obey.\NThat is my opinion!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.80,0:09:08.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore! I sincerely request that\NCaptain Unohana of Squad Four
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.80,0:09:12.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,judge the matter kindly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.44,0:09:18.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This concludes the arrest report\Nfrom Captain Ukitake of Squad 13!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.73,0:09:21.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.62,0:09:24.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,However, the damage caused\Nby these Ryoka,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.99,0:09:27.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,whom you have aided,\Nis substantial.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.98,0:09:33.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In light of your rank\Nand responsibilities,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.79,0:09:36.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot condone your actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.16,0:09:39.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You do understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.34,0:09:43.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Fourteenth Advanced Relief\NGroup Leader
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.47,0:09:47.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and Squad Four,\NSeventh Seat, Hanataro Yamada.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.36,0:10:08.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What’s the matter, Hanataro?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.65,0:10:13.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if what I did was a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.10,0:10:16.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Did I create more trouble\Nfor Rukia instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.97,0:10:17.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.71,0:10:24.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,However, seeing how you act\Nso true to your feelings,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.20,0:10:25.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’m a bit envious of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.87,0:10:27.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.56,0:10:30.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The rest is up to Captain Unohana…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.29,0:11:20.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s go, Zabimaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.71,0:11:45.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I-I drew my sword against\NMiss Hinamori.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.13,0:11:51.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How could I… Despicable…\NI’m…despicable…!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.51,0:12:01.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Burst! Tobiume!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.88,0:12:07.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your head, Wabisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.70,0:12:20.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Who’s there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.32,0:12:23.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.54,0:12:27.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is just awful.\NCan’t bear to look.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.19,0:12:34.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Captain…Ichimaru…!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.74,0:12:42.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You look haggard, poor thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.03,0:12:47.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Want me to help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.40,0:12:51.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, Izuru?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.98,0:13:10.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stand up, Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.52,0:13:18.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Three days! Ichigo,\Nyou don’t have time to dawdle!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.21,0:13:25.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll say it once more.\NStand up, Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.32,0:13:35.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stop stalling!\NAre you going to waste time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.67,0:13:36.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.86,0:13:43.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If he cannot stand on his own…\Nthen I’ll drag him to his feet!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.71,0:13:49.68,OS,Default,0000,0000,0000,,ELEVEN
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.98,0:13:49.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My, was I ever surprised!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.68,0:13:54.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,To think that Lieutenant Kusajishi\Nwould pick me up at that place!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.51,0:13:58.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I, Makizo Aramaki,\Nam moved beyond words!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.66,0:14:01.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well…I didn’t really care about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.62,0:14:03.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let…me…go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.57,0:14:06.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.08,0:14:07.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, I can’t!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.34,0:14:13.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why you--!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.56,0:14:16.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.41,0:14:23.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should apologize\Nwhen she wakes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.32,0:14:33.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Maki-Maki?\NWhat’s that you’re carrying?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.52,0:14:37.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That Spiritual Pressure…\NA Ryoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.96,0:14:42.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No. Well…you see, this, well…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.51,0:14:43.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That’s a Ryoka, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.70,0:14:48.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is, well, umm…\Nthere were circumstances…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.40,0:14:51.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Circumstances? Oh, like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.37,0:14:54.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well…that is…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.31,0:15:01.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This girl, you see…um…\Nshe suddenly spurted out of this area…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.78,0:15:03.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Spurted out?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.25,0:15:05.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes. Like…bubbling.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.72,0:15:07.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Bubbling?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.19,0:15:09.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So I thought it was very unusual,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.39,0:15:11.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and I wanted to show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.92,0:15:12.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.68,0:15:15.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then let’s take her back with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.63,0:15:17.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.36,0:15:20.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see her\Ndoing the bubbling thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.97,0:15:21.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that’s…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.80,0:15:25.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Ichi does\Nthe bubbling too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.47,0:15:29.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ara… Ara… umm…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.20,0:15:32.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ara…what’s your name again?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.17,0:15:36.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Pardon me!\NIt’s Maki-Maki! Maki-Maki is fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.16,0:15:39.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s been ten years since you\Nso kindly took me into your care!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.39,0:15:41.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Maki-Maki…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.62,0:15:43.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hah! That’s a weird name!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.96,0:15:46.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wha--?! But that’s the nickname\Nyou gave me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.13,0:15:51.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So, what’s happening, Orihime?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.04,0:15:53.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She’s beautiful…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.72,0:15:55.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is Ichigo still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.48,0:16:01.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I want him to be alive.\NNo, I’m sure he’s alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.31,0:16:03.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Orihime…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.20,0:16:09.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He’s alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.27,0:16:12.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.72,0:16:16.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He’s alive and he’s trying\Nto get stronger still. Interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.28,0:16:18.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll lend you a hand, woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.05,0:16:22.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If I stick with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.58,0:16:24.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I get the feeling\NI’ll see Ichigo again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.88,0:16:25.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Yep!\N– Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.48,0:16:26.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.53,0:16:30.03,OS,Default,0000,0000,0000,,FOUR
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.64,0:16:46.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Where is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.52,0:16:50.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Am I alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.61,0:16:51.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.13,0:16:57.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.04,0:17:04.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you,\Nwho are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.38,0:17:06.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a burglar, you jerk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.03,0:17:10.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! Why would anyone try to steal\Nfrom an injured man in prison?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.12,0:17:12.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s me, me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.68,0:17:17.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,G-Ganju?! You’re alive! Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.45,0:17:19.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You didn’t seem too strong\Nso I thought maybe…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.98,0:17:24.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That line…\NI’ll throw it right back at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.33,0:17:31.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Still… Why did they treat our injuries?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.20,0:17:36.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We’re intruders and also their enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.87,0:17:41.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There shouldn’t be any reason\Nfor the Soul Society to treat us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.72,0:17:43.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The situation has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.37,0:17:45.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sado.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.97,0:17:48.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I overheard the guard talking\Nand found out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.92,0:17:53.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, a Captain was assassinated\Nwithin the Seireitei.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.23,0:17:55.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The culprit is unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.76,0:17:56.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.72,0:18:01.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So we’re the prime suspects\Nin the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.04,0:18:03.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We’ve been kept alive\Nfor their investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.55,0:18:05.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That’s what it means.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.44,0:18:09.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If only my Spiritual Pressure\Nwasn’t sealed with these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.62,0:18:13.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We could bust right out of here\Nwith my Seppa right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.17,0:18:19.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I see…\NThese seal the Spiritual Pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.64,0:18:22.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Too strong of a flame,\Nand you will burn yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.70,0:18:27.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sanreishuto…\Nyou must never remove this glove.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.95,0:18:28.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you remove the glove,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.76,0:18:31.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,for a moment you will gain\Nenormous powers, however…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.35,0:18:36.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,you will surely lose all\Nyour Quincy powers as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.50,0:18:42.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No. Even without this,\Nmy Spiritual Pressure’s already…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.69,0:18:43.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.16,0:18:47.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Although we did survive,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.44,0:18:50.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,we’re stuck in this prison with\Nour Spiritual Pressure sealed,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.30,0:18:52.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and it really sucks!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.28,0:18:55.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,However, one thing’s for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.12,0:18:59.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,As long as the enemy has\Nno intention of killing us,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.18,0:19:03.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,the rest of the gang is sure\Nto be alive as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.14,0:19:07.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing that we are\Ncaptured like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.99,0:19:10.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,we can assume that Orihime,\Nwho’s not suited for combat,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.92,0:19:12.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,is probably detained somewhere\Nas well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.81,0:19:16.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That leaves just Yoruichi\Nand Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.86,0:19:19.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I will wait for Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.02,0:19:22.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo will come here\Nwithout fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.51,0:19:25.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What we can do until then
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.24,0:19:29.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,is heal our wounds\Nand prepare for the next battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.82,0:19:33.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s wait for Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.20,0:19:44.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Eighteenth sword…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.80,0:19:55.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That’s it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.27,0:19:57.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The real one…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.23,0:20:01.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,has to be this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.77,0:20:07.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Too weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.64,0:20:20.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,As I’ve said. All these swords\Nrepresent a piece of your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.24,0:20:24.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The purpose of this trial is\Nto find the one piece among these
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.44,0:20:27.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,that was forged just\Nfor combat alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.04,0:20:33.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That one there was your “heart’s frailty”\Nfor trying to depend on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.94,0:20:38.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Frailty…my being prone\Nto depending …heart
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.52,0:20:41.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you cannot\Neven discern that,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.93,0:20:44.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,don’t dare mention the word “Bankai!”
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.86,0:20:55.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So these are all my weaknesses…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.17,0:20:56.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.27,0:20:59.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well! Next one, Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.72,0:21:02.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have time\Nto be kneeling!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.27,0:21:04.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.29,0:21:07.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That’s right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.36,0:21:32.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Happy people
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.28,0:21:34.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, come on, come on
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.72,0:21:36.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Happy people
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.24,0:21:38.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.43,0:21:44.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody stand up! Everybody fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.27,0:21:49.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Within your heart, you may feel uneasy
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.26,0:21:53.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But keep your head right up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.64,0:21:55.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,To the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.02,0:21:57.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No matter when (Oh yeah!)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.98,0:22:00.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No matter where (Oh yeah!)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.21,0:22:02.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Just call me anytime! (Oh yeah!)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.44,0:22:04.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll be here for you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.78,0:22:08.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Happy people in the house!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.09,0:22:12.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,With a tough smile
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.38,0:22:17.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Happy people in the house!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.68,0:22:20.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s live!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.27,0:22:22.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wow
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.74,0:22:25.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Happy people in the house
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.62,0:22:26.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.05,0:22:28.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Happy people
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.73,0:22:36.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The food was bad\Nin the Squad Six jail.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.00,0:22:38.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Squad Three's jail didn't\Nget any sunlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.20,0:22:40.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Squad Five's jail had cockroaches!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.36,0:22:42.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There's definitely room\Nfor improvement.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.19,0:22:45.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You guys don't seem to get\Nwhy you were put in jail!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.95,0:22:47.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Why don't you try it, Shiro-chan?\N– I will not!